query:
SELECT id, brand, name, referenceNumber 
FROM watches 
WHERE brand IN ('Rolex', 'Audemars Piguet', 'Patek Philippe', 'Omega', 'IWC', 'Cartier')
AND name IS NOT NULL 
AND name != ''
ORDER BY brand, id
LIMIT 20
